# Template for `.dev.vars` — local secrets consumed by the Wrangler/Vite dev
# runtime (Cloudflare Workers env vars for local dev, NOT `.env`/Vite client
# vars). `.dev.vars*` is gitignored except this example file.
#
# Copy this file to `.dev.vars` and fill in real values before running
# `bun run dev`:
#
#   cp .dev.vars.example .dev.vars

BETTER_AUTH_SECRET=change-me-openssl-rand-hex-16
